Package com.bws.jdistil.core.process

Class ProcessContext

java.lang.Object
com.bws.jdistil.core.process.ProcessContext
public class ProcessContext extends Object
Class used to store data passed from a controlling servlet, such as the DefaultServlet, to classes implementing the Processor interface.
Author:
- Bryan Snipes
